data.description: Welcome to Holly Oak Terrace, an idyllic community in North Wilmington where history meets modern convenience. Nestled less than a quarter-mile from the Delaware River, this fully detached tri-plex presents a unique opportunity to own a home already generating revenue as well as two vacant move-in ready units.  With recent updates, including recent plumbing improvements, this isn't a listing you'll want to miss.  This charming property stands out with its extra-large lot, providing ample off-street parking for all occupants.  Comprising three well-maintained units, each with two bedrooms, this tri-plex boasts a thoughtful layout. The common area entrance grants access to the main floor unit, while a staircase leads to the second floor, offering formal access to units two and three. Unit one enjoys a private entrance through the spacious east-facing porch.  The second-floor unit has recently undergone a refreshing update, making it move-in ready for you or a prime opportunity to place a tenant and generate cash flow. Meanwhile, the third-floor unit offers a unique layout, with interior access and a private exterior entrance via wooden steps from the yard.  The utilities are efficiently managed with electric hot water and baseboard heating, leaving the owner responsible for water/sewer, common area electricity, trash removal, and the maintenance associated with landscaping and snow removal.   This property is an excellent entry point for those beginning their real estate investment journey with this property being well maintained by its current owner. For seasoned investors, it adds a valuable asset to a flourishing portfolio. Alternatively, for a primary resident, living in one unit while letting the other two generate cash flow is an enticing proposition.  Opportunities like this in such a sought-after location are rare, so seize the chance to own a piece of Holly Oak Terrace. Whether you're starting your real estate journey or expanding your portfolio, this tri-plex is a gem waiting for its next chapter. Don't hesitate—schedule a viewing today!
